WEBVTT

00:00:07.716 --> 00:00:11.222
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:00:15.030 --> 00:00:15.999
<i>- Genya!</i>

00:00:16.032 --> 00:00:18.637
- [panting]

00:00:27.855 --> 00:00:29.860
<i>["Kizuna no Kiseki" playing]</i>

00:00:29.893 --> 00:00:37.074
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:01:59.873 --> 00:02:01.877
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:02:11.095 --> 00:02:13.299
- [panting]

00:02:20.782 --> 00:02:22.852
- Gen... ya.

00:02:22.885 --> 00:02:26.292
- [wails]

00:02:26.325 --> 00:02:28.631
What did you strike me with?!

00:02:28.665 --> 00:02:30.801
- I can't regenerate.
<i>- The attack worked.</i>

00:02:30.835 --> 00:02:33.440
- You're pathetic. Calm down!
- ...like I'm being scorched!

00:02:33.473 --> 00:02:35.878
- It'll take more time,
but we can regenerate!

00:02:35.912 --> 00:02:37.414
[Tanjiro gasps]

00:02:37.448 --> 00:02:39.251
<i>I don't know
what's going on with Genya,</i>

00:02:39.285 --> 00:02:41.790
<i>but thanks to him,
I've figured something out.</i>

00:02:41.823 --> 00:02:44.663
<i>Even if we behead
all four at the same time,</i>

00:02:44.696 --> 00:02:47.969
<i>we can't finish them off
like we did Gyutaro.</i>

00:02:48.002 --> 00:02:49.506
[gasps]

00:02:49.540 --> 00:02:52.812
<i>It's almost like attacking them
at all is completely pointless.</i>

00:02:54.081 --> 00:02:55.184
[gasps] Nezuko!

00:02:55.217 --> 00:02:56.987
- [grunting]

00:02:57.020 --> 00:02:58.489
- Nezuko!

00:03:03.902 --> 00:03:05.538
- Nezuko!
- [sighs]

00:03:08.209 --> 00:03:10.948
<i>- Something's been bothering me
all this time.</i>

00:03:12.785 --> 00:03:15.791
<i>Is it possible their neck
isn't their vital spot?</i>

00:03:17.060 --> 00:03:18.597
<i>Something's off.</i>

00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:21.335
<i>That scent I caught
for an instant...</i>

00:03:21.369 --> 00:03:23.974
<i>Right. That was...</i>

00:03:24.007 --> 00:03:25.745
<i>the scent of another demon!</i>

00:03:26.780 --> 00:03:28.083
<i>There's a fifth demon!</i>

00:03:28.116 --> 00:03:30.487
<i>I've got to find it.</i>

00:03:30.521 --> 00:03:32.457
<i>The fifth demon's head's
got to be...</i>

00:03:34.462 --> 00:03:36.867
- [gags]
- Listen, brat!

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:39.807
I'm beating this Upper Rank...

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.644
- by myself!
- Genya!

00:03:41.677 --> 00:03:45.718
- Don't forget there's a reason
you haven't become a Hashira!

00:03:45.751 --> 00:03:49.024
You weren't able to defeat
Upper Rank Six on your own!

00:03:49.058 --> 00:03:50.460
- Oh, uh, okay.

00:03:50.493 --> 00:03:53.634
- And you can bet
your life that...

00:03:53.667 --> 00:03:56.540
I'm going...
to beat you to it!

00:03:56.573 --> 00:03:58.577
- Genya,
what's going on with you?

00:03:58.610 --> 00:03:59.445
You're drooling!

00:03:59.478 --> 00:04:01.249
Not to mention
you're choking me!

00:04:01.282 --> 00:04:02.351
- [creak]
- [winces]

00:04:02.384 --> 00:04:05.257
- I'll be the one
who becomes a Hashira!

00:04:05.290 --> 00:04:07.562
- That's great!
I believe in you!

00:04:07.595 --> 00:04:09.934
You have Nezuko's
and my full support!

00:04:09.967 --> 00:04:11.570
Let's give it our all!

00:04:11.603 --> 00:04:12.772
- Huh?

00:04:12.806 --> 00:04:14.743
- There's a fifth demon
somewhere.

00:04:14.776 --> 00:04:17.448
If you buy me some time,
I can look for it!

00:04:17.481 --> 00:04:20.120
- You're just trying
to get me to let my guard down!

00:04:20.153 --> 00:04:22.592
Don't think I don't know
what you're...

00:04:24.195 --> 00:04:25.564
Huh?

00:04:27.936 --> 00:04:28.904
- [gasps] Look out!

00:04:28.938 --> 00:04:31.943
<i>[thrilling music]</i>

00:04:33.146 --> 00:04:34.916
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:04:34.949 --> 00:04:37.589
<i>[Tanjiro] The Anger Demon's
revived already!</i>

00:04:37.622 --> 00:04:38.758
<i>Hurry!</i>

00:04:38.791 --> 00:04:39.659
Genya!

00:04:39.692 --> 00:04:42.566
I need you to keep
these demons at bay

00:04:42.599 --> 00:04:44.368
while I look for the fifth!

00:04:45.203 --> 00:04:47.842
- Damn it.
They've all regenerated!

00:04:49.445 --> 00:04:52.017
- But whatever you do,
don't slash Nezuko!

00:04:52.050 --> 00:04:54.422
She's my little sister!

00:04:54.455 --> 00:04:55.892
- [grunts]
- Uh...

00:04:55.925 --> 00:04:58.062
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:04:58.095 --> 00:04:59.666
[gunshot]

00:05:02.070 --> 00:05:03.974
<i>- Where's that fifth demon?</i>

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:07.849
<i>I've got to find it</i>

00:05:07.882 --> 00:05:10.420
<i>while Genya and Nezuko
are fending them off.</i>

00:05:15.130 --> 00:05:16.600
- [gasps]

00:05:17.301 --> 00:05:18.537
<i>Hold on.</i>

00:05:18.570 --> 00:05:21.576
<i>Thanks to the wind
created by that fan demon,</i>

00:05:21.610 --> 00:05:24.081
<i>the sulfur smell
from the hot springs is gone.</i>

00:05:24.114 --> 00:05:26.285
- [wind gusts]
<i>- Concentrate...</i>

00:05:26.318 --> 00:05:27.789
<i>and find it!</i>

00:05:27.822 --> 00:05:28.824
[inhales]

00:05:30.661 --> 00:05:31.663
[gasps]

00:05:34.101 --> 00:05:36.540
- [whimpering]

00:05:36.573 --> 00:05:38.410
It's all gonna be okay.

00:05:38.443 --> 00:05:40.915
They'll never find me
in this spot.

00:05:40.948 --> 00:05:42.485
It's all gonna be okay.

00:05:42.519 --> 00:05:44.723
Surely my four Emotions
are strong enough

00:05:44.756 --> 00:05:46.994
to defeat those villains for me!

00:05:47.028 --> 00:05:49.032
<i>- There! Found it!</i>

00:05:49.065 --> 00:05:50.735
<i>Found it! I found it!</i>

00:05:50.768 --> 00:05:52.939
Genya!

00:05:52.973 --> 00:05:54.075
- [growls]

00:05:54.108 --> 00:05:55.109
Urogi!

00:05:58.049 --> 00:05:59.686
- Start heading northeast!

00:06:01.890 --> 00:06:04.730
The fifth demon's hiding
itself close to the ground!

00:06:04.763 --> 00:06:05.898
- Ahh.

00:06:05.932 --> 00:06:07.167
- [growls]

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:09.271
[yells]

00:06:09.304 --> 00:06:11.109
- [gasps]

00:06:11.142 --> 00:06:12.411
Genya!

00:06:12.444 --> 00:06:15.250
You go after it! I'll stay!

00:06:15.283 --> 00:06:16.286
<i>- Northeast!</i>

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:17.420
- Eh?

00:06:18.490 --> 00:06:20.961
<i>[Tanjiro] Crap.
Here comes the lightning.</i>

00:06:22.565 --> 00:06:23.668
- [grunts]
- [groans]

00:06:23.701 --> 00:06:25.872
- Nezuko! Go and help Genya!

00:06:25.905 --> 00:06:29.612
Stop the Lightning Demon
before it gets in Genya's way!

00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:33.319
[gasps]

00:06:33.352 --> 00:06:35.591
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:06:39.231 --> 00:06:42.839
<i>Don't let go! You can't
let yourself get swept away!</i>

00:06:42.872 --> 00:06:43.840
[gasps]

00:06:43.874 --> 00:06:45.376
<i>Oh, no.</i>

00:06:45.410 --> 00:06:47.013
<i>Here comes
that lightning attack!</i>

00:06:48.015 --> 00:06:48.985
[gasps]

00:06:49.018 --> 00:06:51.088
<i>[singer vocalizing]</i>

00:06:51.121 --> 00:06:52.357
- [gasps]

00:06:52.391 --> 00:06:53.861
- [growls]

00:06:53.894 --> 00:06:55.965
[gagging]

00:06:59.171 --> 00:07:02.144
- Nezuko!

00:07:02.177 --> 00:07:06.052
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:07:06.085 --> 00:07:09.258
- Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:07:09.292 --> 00:07:11.664
Is it excruciating?

00:07:11.697 --> 00:07:15.069
It must be excruciating!

00:07:21.349 --> 00:07:23.887
<i>[Tokito] So it's
the same everywhere.</i>

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:25.290
- Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:07:25.323 --> 00:07:27.829
Not only are you
unable to unleash

00:07:27.862 --> 00:07:29.732
your precious
Breathing Techniques,

00:07:29.766 --> 00:07:33.740
but you'll soon be drawing
your last breath in there too!

00:07:37.147 --> 00:07:39.920
[cackles]

00:07:39.953 --> 00:07:42.692
That fake
stoic look on your face,

00:07:42.725 --> 00:07:44.829
how incredibly sublime it is!

00:07:44.862 --> 00:07:50.006
My creative juices are
simply gushing looking upon it!

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:52.243
[Nezuko grunting]

00:07:53.246 --> 00:07:54.282
- Don't fight back.

00:07:54.315 --> 00:07:56.820
You're making me sad.

00:07:56.853 --> 00:07:57.822
Sekido...

00:07:57.856 --> 00:08:00.761
- Hold the girl still
so I can crucify her.

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.236
[gasps]

00:08:11.015 --> 00:08:11.951
<i>That little brat.</i>

00:08:11.984 --> 00:08:14.689
<i>He's gotten
even faster than before!</i>

00:08:15.524 --> 00:08:18.395
<i>No, from the moment
I first met him,</i>

00:08:18.429 --> 00:08:20.199
<i>he's exceeded
my lord's reports.</i>

00:08:20.233 --> 00:08:24.007
<i>He has quick reflexes,
a keen battle sense...</i>

00:08:26.112 --> 00:08:28.083
- [gags]

00:08:28.116 --> 00:08:30.387
<i>- ...and the closer
he is to defeat,</i>

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:31.990
<i>the stronger he gets!</i>

00:08:32.992 --> 00:08:34.328
- [groans]

00:08:34.362 --> 00:08:36.031
- [grunts]

00:08:36.064 --> 00:08:38.603
- [screaming]

00:08:41.041 --> 00:08:42.143
<i>- Damn it.</i>

00:08:42.177 --> 00:08:43.346
<i>Karaku!</i>

00:08:43.380 --> 00:08:44.582
<i>Karaku!</i>

00:08:46.386 --> 00:08:47.354
- [grunts]

00:08:47.387 --> 00:08:49.725
- That's far enough, you punk!

00:08:50.561 --> 00:08:52.330
- [groans]

00:08:52.364 --> 00:08:57.040
- All right! Now to take care
of that trigger-happy kid.

00:08:57.074 --> 00:08:58.075
Huh?

00:08:59.444 --> 00:09:01.950
<i>What?! He still slashed me?!</i>

00:09:03.085 --> 00:09:04.255
You damn punk!

00:09:04.288 --> 00:09:05.658
- Genya!

00:09:05.691 --> 00:09:07.194
To your right!

00:09:07.227 --> 00:09:10.200
It's on your right,
moving south! Search for it!

00:09:10.233 --> 00:09:13.172
<i>- [scoffs] What do
you think I'm doing?</i>

00:09:13.205 --> 00:09:14.809
<i>I've been searching for it!</i>

00:09:14.842 --> 00:09:19.251
<i>A spell? Can I not see it
because of some type of spell?!</i>

00:09:19.285 --> 00:09:21.923
<i>Damn! Damn! Damn!</i>

00:09:21.956 --> 00:09:23.159
<i>Where are you?</i>

00:09:23.193 --> 00:09:24.494
<i>The longer this goes on,</i>

00:09:24.529 --> 00:09:26.866
<i>the closer I get
to being depleted!</i>

00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:28.436
- [grunts]

00:09:28.469 --> 00:09:29.872
- [gags]

00:09:31.309 --> 00:09:32.377
Turn west!

00:09:32.411 --> 00:09:35.149
More to the right!
It's nearby! Below!

00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:38.557
<i>- Where is it?!</i>

00:09:38.591 --> 00:09:39.559
<i>Where?!</i>

00:09:39.593 --> 00:09:41.429
- Genya! Below!

00:09:41.462 --> 00:09:42.598
- [gasps]

00:09:42.631 --> 00:09:45.203
- Huh?
- [whimpering]

00:09:45.236 --> 00:09:47.207
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:09:47.240 --> 00:09:49.679
- It's puny!

00:09:51.315 --> 00:09:52.952
- [shrieks]

00:09:52.985 --> 00:09:55.991
<i>- This is the main body?!
It's so tiny!</i>

00:09:56.025 --> 00:09:59.197
<i>Damn it! How the hell
am I supposed to shoot</i>

00:09:59.231 --> 00:10:00.968
<i>something that moves around
like that?!</i>

00:10:01.001 --> 00:10:04.141
<i>This demon is no bigger
than a field mouse!</i>

00:10:04.174 --> 00:10:06.813
<i>But those other four
are crazy strong!</i>

00:10:06.846 --> 00:10:09.284
<i>This whole time,
he's been controlling them?!</i>

00:10:09.318 --> 00:10:11.523
<i>We have to fight off
four demons at once</i>

00:10:11.556 --> 00:10:13.326
<i>while chasing this mouse!</i>

00:10:13.359 --> 00:10:14.929
<i>What a pain!</i>

00:10:14.962 --> 00:10:17.301
<i>Now I can see why
so many Demon Slayers</i>

00:10:17.334 --> 00:10:18.737
<i>keep ending up dead!</i>

00:10:18.770 --> 00:10:20.875
<i>Don't mess with me,
you annoying runt!</i>

00:10:20.908 --> 00:10:23.379
<i>You're really
starting to piss me off!</i>

00:10:23.412 --> 00:10:25.383
- [wails]

00:10:25.416 --> 00:10:28.155
<i>- I can do this! I can win!</i>

00:10:29.926 --> 00:10:32.899
- [winces]
- [gasps]

00:10:32.932 --> 00:10:35.336
<i>I... can't slash it?</i>

00:10:35.370 --> 00:10:36.573
<i>I can't slash it!</i>

00:10:36.606 --> 00:10:39.344
<i>No way. No way!</i>

00:10:39.377 --> 00:10:40.480
<i>Look at it!</i>

00:10:40.514 --> 00:10:42.952
<i>His head is no bigger
than my finger!</i>

00:10:42.985 --> 00:10:44.288
[growls]

00:10:44.321 --> 00:10:45.924
- [screams]

00:10:46.926 --> 00:10:47.729
- [gasps]

00:10:47.762 --> 00:10:49.231
- [whimpers]

00:10:49.264 --> 00:10:50.434
[squeals]

00:10:50.467 --> 00:10:52.136
<i>- That didn't work?!</i>

00:10:52.170 --> 00:10:53.941
[staff jingles]

00:10:53.974 --> 00:10:54.976
- [gasps]

00:10:56.479 --> 00:10:59.752
<i>Oh, crap. I was too slow!</i>

00:10:59.785 --> 00:11:02.123
<i>I can't get out
of the way!</i>

00:11:02.156 --> 00:11:03.960
<i>I'm gonna die.</i>

00:11:04.930 --> 00:11:07.367
<i>I won't be able
to regenerate my neck.</i>

00:11:11.108 --> 00:11:12.678
<i>Big Brother.</i>

00:11:14.716 --> 00:11:16.051
<i>[sentimental music]</i>

00:11:16.084 --> 00:11:18.957
<i>I wanted to become a Hashira</i>

00:11:18.990 --> 00:11:21.361
<i>so that my big brother
would acknowledge me...</i>

00:11:22.464 --> 00:11:24.902
<i>and so I could
apologize to him...</i>

00:11:25.704 --> 00:11:27.473
<i>for what I said that day.</i>

00:11:29.812 --> 00:11:31.683
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:11:31.716 --> 00:11:33.018
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:11:36.826 --> 00:11:38.697
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:11:38.730 --> 00:11:40.232
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:11:44.675 --> 00:11:46.847
<i>[Genya] I can still remember</i>

00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:49.952
<i>just how small
Mother was back then.</i>

00:11:49.986 --> 00:11:52.056
<i>Even when I was younger,</i>

00:11:52.090 --> 00:11:55.429
<i>I was somehow
already taller than she was.</i>

00:11:56.700 --> 00:11:58.804
<i>From morning 'til night,</i>

00:11:58.837 --> 00:12:01.977
<i>Mother was always
keeping herself busy working.</i>

00:12:02.010 --> 00:12:03.446
<i>Come to think of it,</i>

00:12:03.479 --> 00:12:07.253
<i>not once did I ever see her
take a break or even sleep.</i>

00:12:09.224 --> 00:12:12.397
<i>On the other hand,
my father was a big guy</i>

00:12:12.431 --> 00:12:13.933
<i>and a good-for-nothing.</i>

00:12:14.769 --> 00:12:15.872
<i>He got stabbed to death</i>

00:12:15.905 --> 00:12:18.209
<i>by someone
with a grudge against him.</i>

00:12:18.243 --> 00:12:19.980
<i>Serves him right.</i>

00:12:20.013 --> 00:12:21.950
<i>After all, the old man</i>

00:12:21.984 --> 00:12:25.056
<i>was always beating up
on his own wife and kids.</i>

00:12:26.124 --> 00:12:28.864
<i>Using that tiny body of hers,</i>

00:12:28.897 --> 00:12:31.936
<i>Mother would put herself
between us and our father</i>

00:12:31.970 --> 00:12:35.545
<i>all in order to try and
shield us from his beatings.</i>

00:12:35.578 --> 00:12:37.881
<i>She was an amazing person.</i>

00:12:39.786 --> 00:12:42.558
[insects chirping]

00:12:42.591 --> 00:12:45.797
- [soft snoring]

00:12:58.590 --> 00:13:01.194
- Hey, Mom's late, isn't she?

00:13:02.197 --> 00:13:03.198
- Hmm?

00:13:06.907 --> 00:13:09.546
Genya, you're still awake?

00:13:09.579 --> 00:13:11.348
- Yeah, but so are you.

00:13:11.381 --> 00:13:12.652
- [sighs]

00:13:12.685 --> 00:13:14.755
All right.
I'm going to look for Mom.

00:13:14.789 --> 00:13:16.592
- Wait, I'll go too.

00:13:16.626 --> 00:13:19.666
- No. I want you
to stay home.

00:13:19.699 --> 00:13:21.335
I can do this by myself.

00:13:22.304 --> 00:13:23.506
- Huh?

00:13:24.508 --> 00:13:25.477
- [sighs]

00:13:25.511 --> 00:13:26.680
We promised, remember?

00:13:26.713 --> 00:13:28.784
- [gasps]

00:13:28.817 --> 00:13:30.353
Yeah, of course.

00:13:35.063 --> 00:13:36.733
- Right. I'll be back.

00:13:36.767 --> 00:13:38.169
- [grunts]

00:13:38.202 --> 00:13:40.172
[door slides]

00:13:48.055 --> 00:13:49.759
- [laughter]
- Huh?

00:13:49.793 --> 00:13:51.228
- Brother!

00:13:52.230 --> 00:13:53.232
- Brother!

00:13:54.234 --> 00:13:55.269
- Brother!

00:13:55.303 --> 00:13:57.106
- Brother.

00:13:58.610 --> 00:14:00.514
- [chuckles] What gives?

00:14:00.548 --> 00:14:02.918
Why are all you guys awake too?

00:14:05.323 --> 00:14:06.760
- [soft breathing]

00:14:06.793 --> 00:14:09.766
- You promise
you think Mom's okay?

00:14:09.799 --> 00:14:11.837
- She's fine, all right?

00:14:11.870 --> 00:14:14.675
Big Bro just went
to look for her to make sure.

00:14:14.708 --> 00:14:16.144
- Yeah, but...

00:14:17.882 --> 00:14:19.117
- It's so late.

00:14:19.151 --> 00:14:21.990
She's never been out
this long at night, has she?

00:14:22.023 --> 00:14:25.798
The sun's
already about to come up.

00:14:25.831 --> 00:14:27.701
- It's gonna be okay.

00:14:27.735 --> 00:14:29.104
I bet you're tired.

00:14:29.137 --> 00:14:31.375
Go back to bed. You'll see.

00:14:31.408 --> 00:14:34.481
Mom and Big Brother
will be back by morning.

00:14:34.516 --> 00:14:36.820
[wall clatters]

00:14:36.853 --> 00:14:39.358
- [gasps] That must be her!

00:14:39.391 --> 00:14:40.560
- Mom!

00:14:40.594 --> 00:14:41.763
- Mom!
- Mom!

00:14:41.796 --> 00:14:43.065
- [shudders]

00:14:44.468 --> 00:14:46.038
Wait! Don't open it!

00:14:46.071 --> 00:14:47.908
It might not be Mom
that's at the--

00:14:49.444 --> 00:14:50.614
[gasps]

00:14:50.647 --> 00:14:52.283
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:14:52.316 --> 00:14:56.057
[wails]

00:14:57.494 --> 00:14:58.864
- [snarls]

00:14:58.897 --> 00:15:02.037
<i>- Is it a beast? A stray dog?</i>

00:15:02.070 --> 00:15:03.439
<i>No, it's a wolf!</i>

00:15:04.676 --> 00:15:07.280
<i>It's too dark to see!</i>

00:15:07.313 --> 00:15:08.449
<i>It's fast!</i>

00:15:09.719 --> 00:15:11.121
- Genya, run away!

00:15:11.990 --> 00:15:13.392
- Brother!

00:15:13.425 --> 00:15:16.298
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:15:16.332 --> 00:15:17.500
[shudders]

00:15:19.672 --> 00:15:20.874
[gasps]

00:15:20.907 --> 00:15:23.547
No! Koto!

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:24.916
Shuya!

00:15:24.949 --> 00:15:28.155
Hiroshi! Teiko! Sumi!

00:15:29.859 --> 00:15:32.497
Put pressure on your wounds!

00:15:32.531 --> 00:15:34.167
I'll go get the doctor!

00:15:34.200 --> 00:15:36.138
Just hang on a little longer!

00:15:37.842 --> 00:15:40.413
[footsteps crunching]

00:15:40.446 --> 00:15:42.818
[panting]

00:15:42.851 --> 00:15:45.624
<i>I don't know what's going on.</i>

00:15:45.657 --> 00:15:47.695
<i>What was that thing back there?</i>

00:15:47.728 --> 00:15:48.831
<i>And where's Brother?</i>

00:15:48.864 --> 00:15:51.702
<i>No, I have to get
the doctor first!</i>

00:15:58.049 --> 00:15:59.250
Brother...

00:16:02.658 --> 00:16:03.794
[gasps]

00:16:03.827 --> 00:16:04.862
Mother!

00:16:04.895 --> 00:16:07.834
[sobbing]

00:16:07.868 --> 00:16:10.039
Mother! Mother!

00:16:10.072 --> 00:16:11.441
Why'd you do it?

00:16:11.475 --> 00:16:12.611
Why'd you do it?!

00:16:12.645 --> 00:16:15.584
What made you
want to kill our own mother?!

00:16:15.617 --> 00:16:17.555
[sobbing]

00:16:17.588 --> 00:16:18.590
Murderer!

00:16:19.592 --> 00:16:23.766
You murderer!

00:16:25.469 --> 00:16:28.677
<i>I'm sorry I said
those awful things, Brother.</i>

00:16:28.710 --> 00:16:29.879
<i>Forgive me.</i>

00:16:29.912 --> 00:16:32.083
<i>It's all--</i>

00:16:32.116 --> 00:16:34.955
<i>It's all just excuses, but...</i>

00:16:34.989 --> 00:16:36.391
<i>I was in a panic.</i>

00:16:37.595 --> 00:16:41.870
<i>Shuya, Hiroshi,
Koto, Teiko, and Sumi</i>

00:16:41.903 --> 00:16:43.907
<i>were all lying there dead,</i>

00:16:43.941 --> 00:16:45.476
<i>not answering me.</i>

00:16:46.679 --> 00:16:48.048
<i>"It's over."</i>

00:16:48.081 --> 00:16:51.556
<i>In that very moment,
I knew I would die next.</i>

00:16:52.758 --> 00:16:54.361
<i>And that rabid wolf...</i>

00:16:55.263 --> 00:16:58.236
<i>Or at least
what I thought was a wolf...</i>

00:16:58.269 --> 00:17:01.241
<i>was our mother,
who'd turned into a demon.</i>

00:17:03.079 --> 00:17:06.385
<i>You risked your life
fighting her to protect us</i>

00:17:06.418 --> 00:17:08.957
<i>and carried her outside
towards daybreak.</i>

00:17:08.990 --> 00:17:12.397
<i>That moment,
when you first realized</i>

00:17:12.430 --> 00:17:15.269
<i>that it was Mom
who was attacking our family...</i>

00:17:16.706 --> 00:17:20.246
<i>I can't imagine how that
made you feel, Brother.</i>

00:17:21.314 --> 00:17:24.855
<i>Standing there
lifeless and shattered</i>

00:17:24.889 --> 00:17:27.360
<i>after killing
our beloved mother</i>

00:17:27.394 --> 00:17:31.468
<i>and having your brother that you
fought to protect denounce you,</i>

00:17:31.503 --> 00:17:33.941
<i>I can't imagine
how that made you feel.</i>

00:17:33.974 --> 00:17:35.076
<i>[shudders]</i>

00:17:35.110 --> 00:17:38.181
<i>When we'd just promised
each other</i>

00:17:38.215 --> 00:17:41.622
<i>that we'd do everything
we could to protect our family.</i>

00:17:45.964 --> 00:17:49.137
[birds calling]

00:17:54.481 --> 00:17:55.450
- Genya?

00:17:55.483 --> 00:17:56.418
- Huh?

00:17:57.420 --> 00:18:00.326
- It's up to us now
to protect the family.

00:18:00.359 --> 00:18:01.194
- Uh...

00:18:01.228 --> 00:18:03.666
- Dad got himself killed,
after all.

00:18:03.700 --> 00:18:06.706
And while things will be
easier without him around...

00:18:07.874 --> 00:18:13.485
without a father, everyone might
start to feel hopeless.

00:18:13.519 --> 00:18:15.322
- [sighs]

00:18:16.492 --> 00:18:20.133
From now on,
it's up to you and me

00:18:20.166 --> 00:18:23.305
to do our best to protect
our whole family.

00:18:24.474 --> 00:18:25.611
Got that?

00:18:25.644 --> 00:18:27.413
- [gasps]

00:18:27.446 --> 00:18:28.549
[sighs]

00:18:29.885 --> 00:18:33.025
But we always have,
haven't we?

00:18:33.059 --> 00:18:35.897
Now's no different. Right, Bro?

00:18:38.803 --> 00:18:39.805
[grunts]

00:18:41.509 --> 00:18:42.745
- [chuckles]

00:18:42.778 --> 00:18:44.515
[laughs]

00:18:46.920 --> 00:18:49.457
<i>- I'm sorry, Brother.</i>

00:18:49.490 --> 00:18:52.764
<i>I'm going to die without
getting a chance to apologize.</i>

00:18:54.502 --> 00:18:57.675
<i>Even with my life
flashing before my eyes,</i>

00:18:57.708 --> 00:19:00.814
<i>that memory of you smiling
is at the front of my mind.</i>

00:19:00.847 --> 00:19:03.486
<i>I'm not like you, Brother.</i>

00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:05.691
<i>I don't have
any talents of my own.</i>

00:19:05.724 --> 00:19:08.228
<i>I can't use
Breathing Techniques,</i>

00:19:08.262 --> 00:19:10.366
<i>and I'll never become
a Hashira.</i>

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:15.744
<i>And if I never become one,
I'll never meet other Hashira.</i>

00:19:15.777 --> 00:19:19.484
<i>I gave it my all,
but it wasn't enough.</i>

00:19:20.386 --> 00:19:22.558
- A scumbag like yourself

00:19:22.591 --> 00:19:25.029
could never be
a brother of mine.

00:19:25.062 --> 00:19:26.832
You're better off
quitting the Corps.

00:19:28.670 --> 00:19:30.005
<i>- You don't mean that.</i>

00:19:30.039 --> 00:19:33.278
<i>I may have changed, but I'm
still your younger brother!</i>

00:19:34.080 --> 00:19:35.717
[Tanjiro] Genya!

00:19:36.719 --> 00:19:37.855
You can't give up!

00:19:37.888 --> 00:19:38.890
- [gasps]

00:19:40.126 --> 00:19:41.729
- [gags]

00:19:41.763 --> 00:19:43.265
- [winces]

00:19:43.298 --> 00:19:45.838
- Try again!
- [gasps]

00:19:45.871 --> 00:19:47.608
- Try slashing it again!

00:19:47.641 --> 00:19:50.947
You gotta keep trying!
You can't give up!

00:19:50.981 --> 00:19:52.884
- [gasps]
- I'll protect you!

00:19:53.920 --> 00:19:56.257
Concentrate solely
on beheading it!

00:19:57.193 --> 00:19:59.030
Aren't you gonna
become a Hashira?

00:19:59.063 --> 00:20:01.367
Genya Shinazugawa!

00:20:04.040 --> 00:20:05.009
- [gasps]

00:20:05.042 --> 00:20:07.079
<i>- Oh, no. Behind us!</i>

00:20:07.113 --> 00:20:09.417
- Weeping Spears.

00:20:11.889 --> 00:20:12.958
<i>- This is bad.</i>

00:20:12.992 --> 00:20:15.029
<i>He hit me dead on.</i>

00:20:15.062 --> 00:20:16.532
[winces]

00:20:19.137 --> 00:20:20.339
Huh?

00:20:22.076 --> 00:20:23.311
[gasps]

00:20:24.114 --> 00:20:25.116
- Go.

00:20:25.149 --> 00:20:26.519
- [gasps]

00:20:26.552 --> 00:20:28.055
Genya!

00:20:28.089 --> 00:20:30.292
- [raspy breathing]

00:20:32.296 --> 00:20:35.235
I can't behead it.

00:20:36.773 --> 00:20:39.277
It has to be you...

00:20:39.310 --> 00:20:40.613
who does it!

00:20:41.816 --> 00:20:43.820
So just this one time,

00:20:43.853 --> 00:20:44.922
I'm going...

00:20:46.693 --> 00:20:47.727
- Genya.

00:20:52.136 --> 00:20:53.906
- ...to let you have it!

00:20:58.816 --> 00:21:00.820
[breathes heavily]

00:21:02.090 --> 00:21:03.225
[growls]

00:21:03.258 --> 00:21:05.096
[gunshot echoes]

00:21:05.129 --> 00:21:07.634
<i>- I'll do it. No matter what!</i>

00:21:07.667 --> 00:21:08.970
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:21:09.003 --> 00:21:13.947
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:13.980 --> 00:21:15.349
[gasps]

00:21:15.382 --> 00:21:16.652
- [whimpering]

00:21:16.685 --> 00:21:17.687
<i>- There it is!</i>

00:21:20.025 --> 00:21:21.294
<i>It's tiny!</i>

00:21:24.702 --> 00:21:26.572
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:26.606 --> 00:21:28.843
<i>You're not getting away!</i>

00:21:30.947 --> 00:21:31.916
[footstep scrapes]

00:21:31.949 --> 00:21:33.285
- [gasps]

00:21:33.319 --> 00:21:35.355
[whimpers]

00:21:36.959 --> 00:21:38.963
- [yells]

00:21:42.905 --> 00:21:44.876
<i>["Koi Kogare" playing]</i>

00:21:44.909 --> 00:21:51.922
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:23:12.917 --> 00:23:14.521
[page rustles]

00:23:14.554 --> 00:23:17.460
- Genya, you didn't
have anything to eat today.

00:23:17.493 --> 00:23:18.796
Are you all right?

00:23:18.830 --> 00:23:20.600
I hear that you
haven't actually eaten

00:23:20.633 --> 00:23:22.805
since we met
at the Butterfly Mansion.

00:23:22.838 --> 00:23:25.376
- You can't fight demons
on an empty stomach.

00:23:25.409 --> 00:23:26.545
[girls] Yeah, that's right!

00:23:26.579 --> 00:23:28.081
- I said I don't want anything!

00:23:29.184 --> 00:23:30.687
- You're always acting
too buddy-buddy.

00:23:30.720 --> 00:23:31.789
- 'Cause we're friends!

00:23:31.823 --> 00:23:33.793
- What makes you think
we're friends?!

00:23:33.827 --> 00:23:35.730
- We soaked in the hot springs
together!

00:23:35.764 --> 00:23:37.701
- Look, that was only
because you barged in!

00:23:37.734 --> 00:23:39.572
- And our final selection class!

00:23:39.605 --> 00:23:42.009
That makes us friends, right?

00:23:42.042 --> 00:23:43.412
- Uh...

00:23:43.445 --> 00:23:45.984
Look here,
I told you to stop being so--

00:23:46.018 --> 00:23:46.786
- Hold that thought!

00:23:46.819 --> 00:23:49.357
- Next, Episode 7,
"Awful Villain."

00:23:49.391 --> 00:23:51.060
Genya,
let's always be friends!

00:23:51.094 --> 00:23:52.096
- We're not friends!

